  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd  \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gunshots in the kitchen of Indrani's house",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Shotgun shells wrapped in polythene wrapped in a pot in the kitchen of a house in Kappapilau area, Mullaitivu, were recovered yesterday (24).",
        "When they took it thinking it was a food packet, they found gunshots inside.",
        "All are found to be brand new firearms and the family has informed the Mulliyawela police about the incident following the fear of who brought it.",
        "The incident took place at the house of Indrani, who has been protesting for the release of her land, which has been in the possession of the soldiers for a long time, in Kappapilau area.",
        "Even though their house and land in front of the Kappapilau army camp has been liberated by the army, another of their native land has been occupied by the army and the resources there are being used by the army.",
        "In this case, these people who fought for their land in the past are still demanding to expel the soldiers from their own land and restore their land.",
        "In this case, Indrani has said that how the gun came into his house has caused surprise and has also caused suspicion."
      ],
